<p><b>What is a daily devotional practice?</b> The Power of Daily Devotionals At its essence, daily devotional practice is akin to watering the garden of the soul. It's a dedicated, quiet time, free from the pandemonium of daily life, where one can immerse themselves in prayer and introspection.</p>
